{"tid":1634992,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[警世] 如果我地唔覺意笑、屌得同路人太過分，就請回望我地既烈士！","createTime":"2019-10-07T11:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:30:07.000Z","uid":161430,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d666b58016caa8e6f51fd98946be19250dfb6d86","tid":1634992,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/15/nDpB7Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F15%2FnDpB7Y.png&h=0b6b37ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2375000/2377748/0616_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2375000%2F2377748%2F0616_1024.jpeg&h=042642fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仲好記得，6.16果日經過PP，<br />\n果種絕對玩唔倒膠，笑唔出，絕對沉重既感覺，<br />\n我亦都記得，點解有二百萬，其實有一半都係前一晚比梁烈士谷出去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/q_5hDC6_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fq_5hDC6_1200x0.png&h=c1b51337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二百萬零一人，多謝你。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkusu.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1-8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkusu.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F1-8.jpg&h=115a2ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係好可惜，之後仲有更多手足選擇行呢條路。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/06/30/2838180_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F06%2F30%2F2838180_1.jpg&h=c4e891b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但好多謝你，我地會堅持落去，雖然中間成日會忍唔住鬧交，包括我，太衝動去鬧人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/06/30/2838180_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F06%2F30%2F2838180_3.jpg&h=86cd96ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港需要的是革命，我地收到喇，多謝你既心意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tnimage.taiwannews.com.tw/photos/2019/07/05/1562294650-5d1eb97a4e6d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftnimage.taiwannews.com.tw%2Fphotos%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F1562294650-5d1eb97a4e6d1.jpg&h=b71f79f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個人要走之前，仲留低呢d野，大家可以想像到，佢決心有幾咁大。<br />\n<br />\n呢位手足輕生前，甚至曾經鼓勵男急救員加油，唔好放棄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2019/09/d4350818-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2Fd4350818-800x450.jpg&h=a8e4d7fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我一直唔明白，一個人決定走之前，唔係通常都好絕望？好灰，<br />\n究竟要點樣勇敢同偉大，先可以喺走之前仲不忘叫人加油，唔好放棄？<br />\n<br />\n不分次序，其實仲有以下等 總共九名烈士，我都會記住，都會多謝你地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/4/40/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B_ZhitaWu_fbmsg.png/revision/latest?cb=20190630142159\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F4%2F40%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B_ZhitaWu_fbmsg.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20190630142159&h=37f7d648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地重新出發啦，緊記和勇合一，<br />\n緊記除左五大訴求係初衷，<br />\n仲有一句話，我地由四個月前就開始講:<br />\n<br />\n「兄弟爬山，各自努力」<br />\n<br />\n今晚8點見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4a15e1a12ac4752c06157325298556e7a48096e","tid":1634992,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"「兄弟爬山，各自努力」<br />\n<br />\n今晚8點見！"},{"pid":"941b7c93392ec67b00b4ec4317655d563671e571","tid":1634992,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:11:59.000Z","msg":"We are temporarily using live channel直播台as english channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634498\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634498</a><br />\n<br />\n[國際戰線] 連登開左英文台！English Channel is LIVE now on LIHKG!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634824\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634824</a>"},{"pid":"80ba8ec23daff8d15a68a358297ea538183c911d","tid":1634992,"uid":115769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"Push, 多謝所有出過力既香港人"},{"pid":"ef41da62c9e48caa189d151f963e42d8573f8086","tid":1634992,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ugsGBd9wmOA/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FugsGBd9wmOA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=5e9a34b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"156c01079ce3be510522feb8621cbb12e1e8ffc2","tid":1634992,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd748fb288fcc90de373ad45ca01f8be6248cfe","tid":1634992,"uid":56518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"你哋配唔配擁有民主？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634946</a>"},{"pid":"02d403fb2146ec41731a5a26c7cb8b675a8f86c3","tid":1634992,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/201907051212430501_AG091.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F201907051212430501_AG091.jpg&h=50877869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D9Ha2EsVAAEIWlf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD9Ha2EsVAAEIWlf.jpg&h=efdb3971&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb77f373b385aa0ce266dd28ea19514c5749c4ac","tid":1634992,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4a15e1a12ac4752c06157325298556e7a